title: Memelas and Thai Bistro
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A Thai and Mexican food restaurant. Veggie items are tortilla soup, tom yum and tom kha soups with vegetables or tofu, spicy noodles with tofu and vegetables, mock duck, tofu burrito, a portabello torta and taco, pineapple fried rice with tofu, and several other Thai entrees that can be requested with tofu and veggies in place of meat. Prices cheap to moderate depending on what you order.
